Python Sys Hooks:
excepthook              # (type, value, traceback)
breakpointhook          # called by breakpoint(*args, **kwargs). usually pdb.set_trace
displayhook             # (value)
unraisablehook          # (tuple(exc_type, exc_value, exc_traceback, err_msg, obj))

sys.exception()         # -> current Exception.
sys.audit(event, *args) # raise auditing event
sys.addaudithook(fn)    # add a hook.
